title: Changsow Vegetarian
description: Vegetarian restaurant serving a wide variety of Indonesian and other Asian foods. Many mock-meat choices (most likely vegan but please inquire). Serves freshly made-in-house juices. While the address is on K H Mansyur, the entrance is around the corner on JL Pekapuran. Many locals know the place and will direct you.
streetAddress: JL K H Mansyur No 120 B-F-G, Jembatan Lima
